Subject: [PATCH] Adjusting nvidia-settings paths

Adding the correct path to the nvidia-settings binary.

Fixed path to nvidia-settings icon. It is now displayed based on your current icon theme.
See details: https://github.com/NVIDIA/nvidia-settings/pull/56
---
 nvidia-settings.desktop | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/nvidia-settings.desktop b/nvidia-settings.desktop
index 2957dc2..2a45b59 100644
--- a/nvidia-settings.desktop
+++ b/nvidia-settings.desktop
@@ -3,8 +3,8 @@ Type=Application
 Encoding=UTF-8
 Name=NVIDIA X Server Settings
 Comment=Configure NVIDIA X Server Settings
-Exec=__UTILS_PATH__/nvidia-settings
-Icon=__PIXMAP_PATH__/nvidia-settings.png
+Exec=/usr/bin/nvidia-settings
+Icon=nvidia-settings
 Categories=Settings;HardwareSettings;
 
